fields.description: TAG Heuer stirred up quite a surprise when it launched its first Avant-Garde eyewear collection which takes its unique style from the pureness of its design, the development of high-tech materials combining lightness, resistance and performance and from ergonomics which offers exceptional comfort. All TAG Heuer Avant-Garde Eyewear, including the LRS line of sunglasses, feature lenses that are shatter-resistant, ultra-light and provide 100% UV-A and UV-B protection. Tag Heuer LRS sunglasses are so comfortable and lightweight, you may forget you're wearing them. These Tag Heuer sunglasses feature two tone colored, straight, elastomer temples for comfort and easy fit and flexible hinges, ensuring a secure fit on your face. Tag Heuer LRS sunglasses have a high-end finish that reminds you of the premium quality level you'd expect from Tag Heuer glasses. The LRS are optimal for those looking for a clean, sporty, and comfortable wear.
